Text: obituaryForwarded by Tory BracyCorpEnron on PM Nyna K Kent on AM To Alina Bolua Angie Lathan Carla Home Debbies Work Evelyn Cherny Irma Arevalo Tory NRON cc Subject obituary Kathy had just become a widow and needed to put an obituary in the paper about her late husband Anthony She called the newspaper and asked how much to put an obituary in the paper The cost is per word said the newspaper editor Fine please print Bubba died The startled newspaper editor explained that there was a word minimum charge Kathy thought for a moment then said Okay then please print Bubba died pickup truck for sale
